0.9.1.name: wordpress/spiritual-gifts-survey
0.9.1.description: The Spiritual Gifts Survey gives a 128 question test and ranks the gifts based on the test score. In addition, the optional S.H.A.P.E. portion of the survey uses Saddleback Church's S.H.A.P.E. model of Spiritual Gifts, Heart, Abilities, Personality, and Experience to help reveal how God as already shaped you for serving Him.
